description: The fund is an actively managed exchange-traded fund (ETF) that invests in U.S. listed equity securities that have high growth potential based on a low marginal cost business model. It’s investment universe consists of publicly traded equity securities listed in the United States with a minimum market capitalization of $800 million. The Sub-Adviser also excludes REITs, Business Development Companies (“BDCs”), American Depository Receipts (“ADRs”) and Global Depository Receipts (“GDRs”).
name: AOT Growth and Innovation ETF
